Class DescriptorLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat.protobuf.schema.DescriptorLoader

    Class used for loading protobuf descriptors (from .desc files or equivalent sources), to construct FileDescriptorSet.
